[Student "S"]
{Would you really bid over 1NT with only 5 HCP? In the balancing seat you should. Partner is marked with a pretty good hand, and you have a 6-card Major suit.

You do bid just 2\S though, rather than a double followed by 2\S, which would show a stronger hand. Everybody passes.}

